{"tid":682230,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"香港書店已被中聯辦完全控制","createTime":"2018-05-28T16:43:53.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-30T17:03:49.000Z","uid":104096,"like":85,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":44,"replies":[{"pid":"f490bf510b6bb8f475bae5b4a8abeded093e3c6b","tid":682230,"uid":104096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-28T16:43:53.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://www.rthk.hk/tv/dtt31/programme/hkcc/episode/494749\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.rthk.hk%2Ftv%2Fdtt31%2Fprogramme%2Fhkcc%2Fepisode%2F494749&d=XtMOyMlXL4rulnteGpLBtdU7RO4jIL0fLOArxO5LqtQ%3D&h=6a8ba35d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.rthk.hk/tv/dtt31/programme/hkcc/episode/494749</a><br />\n在香港，每年都有幾千本書出版。書店林立，各種各樣的書目不暇給，但原來香港超過一半的書店，來自同一集團。香港還有五大出版社，有三間來自此集團。誰在經營這龐大的出版和書店集團？和中央政府有沒有關係？鏗鏘集展開調查。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">中聯辦真係好撚癲屌你老母</span></span>"},{"pid":"f3805c4faa41750764e107338b8db5c48fe9ae09","tid":682230,"uid":104096,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-28T16:45:22.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1423eb5751ff26c1fe63e9b98309084b6cab79dc","tid":682230,"uid":104096,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-28T16:47:04.000Z","msg":"推推推推"},{"pid":"5d3306678f1222874689311c76e51b59f2c8bfdc","tid":682230,"uid":84783,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-28T16:48:06.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7935088eaab57cae14c6d7aec179e1cf93cc339e","tid":682230,"uid":104096,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5d3306678f1222874689311c76e51b59f2c8bfdc","tid":682230,"uid":84783,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-28T16:48:06.000Z","msg":"推"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-28T16:48:34.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"27fed4a98fa62b81e9e2c36080e2b8b87c4b9ac8","tid":682230,"uid":72186,"like":3,"dislike":3,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-28T16:48:40.000Z","msg":"出版自由 bye<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\"